Package: etvpn-sqluserportal
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         etvpn (= ${binary:Version})
Description: ETVPN Authenticator User Self-Service Portal
 Provides a web portal that allows ETVPN Authenticator SQL based users
 to change their passwords. The portal is composed by a daemon and a
 PSGI web interface.

